nnoremap <Leader>/ :grep<Space>
nnoremap gh :diffget //2<CR>
nnoremap gl :diffget //3<CR>
tnoremap <C-v><Esc> <Esc>

" use <C-z> as wild character in mappings, because we can't use <Tab>
